    "romaji": "Tsugi no bunshou o yonde, shitsumon ni kotaenasai.\n\n[Borantia boshuu no oshirase]\nAozora Toshokan dewa, kodomo-tachi ni hon o yonde ageru 'Yomikikase borantia' o boshuu shite imasu.\n\n1. Taishou: Kono machi ni sunde iru 18-sai ijou no kata. Keiken wa toimasen.\n2. Nichiji: Maitsuki dai-ni, dai-yon doyoubi 14:00-15:00\n3. Boshuu ninjuu: 5-mei\n\nKibou suru kata wa, sangatsu hatsuka made ni denwa de moushikonde kudasai. Teiin ni nari shidai, shimekirimasu.",
